IoskeleyMono (monospace font family)

IoskeleyMono is a monospace font family inspired by Iosevka,
designed for terminals, editors and programming environments.

This package includes the following upstream variants:

  - IoskeleyMono
  - IoskeleyMono-Term
  - IoskeleyMono-NL
  - IoskeleyMono-Web

Normal, SemiCondensed and Condensed widths are included,
together with both hinted and unhinted TrueType fonts.

The Web package provides WOFF2 fonts intended for browser
and web usage.
